    "description": "<p>Import WPNexa templates with just one click. For more information, please visit <a href="https://wpnexa.com/how-it-works" target="_blank">https://wpnexa.com/how-it-works</a>",
    "installation": "<ol><li>Download the <strong>WPNexa Importer</strong> plugin ZIP file.</li><li>Go to your WordPress dashboard.</li><li>Navigate to <strong>Plugins > Add New</strong>.</li><li>Click <strong>Upload Plugin</strong>.</li><li>Select the <code>wpnexa-importer.zip</code> file and click <strong>Install Now</strong>.</li><li>After installation, click <strong>Activate Plugin</strong>.</li></ol>",
